itutes a new well-controlled reference for testing\ntheoretical models of the parton passage through the QGP.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 15 Jan 2018 18:06:10 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 15 Dec 2018 08:36:47 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-12-19"}
