rements of the HI and HeII\nLyman-$\\alpha$ forest opacities. We also present \"equivalent-equilibrium\"\nionization/heating rates that mimic our fiducial UVB model for use in\nsimulation codes that assume ionization equilibrium.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 15 Jan 2018 19:00:00 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-01-30"}
