s efficiently evolve towards coalescence during the\ninteraction with a sequence of individual gas pockets.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 15 Jan 2018 19:00:05 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 22 Jan 2018 10:41:02 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 27 Jun 2018 18:24:40 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-06-29"}
