ate that interband $s$-$d$ interaction, which is\nweak in Mo, increases with the increasing $x$ and influences the nature of\nsuperconductivity in the alloys with higher $x$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 16 Jan 2018 01:19:07 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-01-17"}
