 form satellite systems of small bodies.\nIt is likely that the ratio of the number of rarefied preplanetesimals with\nsuch angular momenta to the total number of rarefied preplanetesimals producing\nclassical trans-Neptunian objects with diameters larger than 100 km was 0.45\n(the initial fraction of satellite systems among all classical trans-Neptunian\nobjects).\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 16 Jan 2018 11:51:59 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-01-17"}
